{"title":"数据结构代码实现：二叉树的遍历","uid":"395b448d9d7bd2d8a1561bdedabff9ce","slug":"DataStructure-BiTree","date":"2020-05-14T08:09:07.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:09.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-BiTree.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200514161206.png","content":"<h2 id=\"二叉树的定义\"><a href=\"#二叉树的定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二叉树的定义\"></a>二叉树的定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">typedef char BiElemType;\ntypedef struct BiTNode&#123;\n    BiElemType data;\n    struct BiTNode *lchild,*rchild;\n&#125;BiTNode,*BiTree;\n&#x2F;&#x2F;链表\ntypedef struct tag&#123;\n    BiTree p;\n    struct tag *pnext;\n&#125;tag_t,*ptag_t;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"层次建树\"><a href=\"#层次建树\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"层次建树\"></a>层次建树</h2><p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200514175300.png\" alt=\"层次建树\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">&#x2F;*\n * 建树\n *&#x2F;\nvoid creatTree(BiTree &amp;tree)&#123;\n    BiTree pnew;\n    int i,j,pos;\n    char c;\n    ptag_t phead&#x3D;NULL,ptail&#x3D;NULL,listpnew,pcur;\n    while(scanf(&quot;%c&quot;,&amp;c)!&#x3D;EOF)&#123;\n        if(c&#x3D;&#x3D;&#39;\\n&#39;)&#123;\n            break;\n        &#125;\n        pnew&#x3D;(BiTree)calloc(1,sizeof(BiTNode));\n        pnew-&gt;data&#x3D;c;\n        listpnew&#x3D;(ptag_t)calloc(1,sizeof(tag_t));\n        listpnew-&gt;p&#x3D;pnew;\n        if(NULL&#x3D;&#x3D;tree)&#123;\n            tree&#x3D;pnew;\n            phead&#x3D;listpnew;&#x2F;&#x2F;链表头\n            ptail&#x3D;listpnew;&#x2F;&#x2F;链表尾\n            pcur&#x3D;listpnew;\n            continue;\n        &#125;else&#123;\n            ptail-&gt;pnext&#x3D;listpnew;&#x2F;&#x2F;通过尾插法，将新结点放入链表\n            ptail&#x3D;listpnew;\n        &#125;\n        if(NULL&#x3D;&#x3D;pcur-&gt;p-&gt;lchild)&#123;\n            pcur-&gt;p-&gt;lchild&#x3D;pnew;\n        &#125;else if(NULL&#x3D;&#x3D;pcur-&gt;p-&gt;rchild)&#123;\n            pcur-&gt;p-&gt;rchild&#x3D;pnew;\n            pcur&#x3D;pcur-&gt;pnext;\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"先序遍历\"><a href=\"#先序遍历\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"先序遍历\"></a>先序遍历</h2><ul>\n<li>若二叉树为空，则什么都不做，否则</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>访问根结点</li>\n<li>先序遍历左子树</li>\n<li>先序遍历右子树 <pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">&#x2F;*\n * 前序遍历\n *&#x2F;\nvoid PreOrder(BiTree T)&#123;\n    if(T!&#x3D;NULL)&#123;\n        putchar(T-&gt;data);\n        PreOrder(T-&gt;lchild);\n        PreOrder(T-&gt;rchild);\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"中序遍历\"><a href=\"#中序遍历\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"中序遍历\"></a>中序遍历</h2></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>若二叉树为空，则什么都不做，否则</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>中序遍历左子树</li>\n<li>访问根结点</li>\n<li>中序遍历左子树<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">&#x2F;*\n * 中序遍历\n *&#x2F;\nvoid InOrder(BiTree T)&#123;\n    if(T!&#x3D;NULL)&#123;\n        InOrder(T-&gt;lchild);\n        putchar(T-&gt;data);\n        InOrder(T-&gt;rchild);\n    &#125;\n&#125;\n&#x2F;*\n * 中序遍历非递归\n *&#x2F;\nvoid InOrder2(BiTree T)&#123;\n    SqStack S;\n    InitStack(S);\n    BiTree p&#x3D;T;\n    while (p||!StackEmpty(S))&#123;\n        if(p)&#123;\n            Push(S,p);\n            p&#x3D;p-&gt;lchild;\n        &#125;else&#123;\n            Pop(S,p);\n            putchar(p-&gt;data);\n            p&#x3D;p-&gt;rchild;\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"后序遍历\"><a href=\"#后序遍历\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"后序遍历\"></a>后序遍历</h2></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>若二叉树为空，则什么都不做，否则</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>后序遍历左子树</li>\n<li>后序遍历左子树</li>\n<li>访问根结点<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">&#x2F;*\n * 后序遍历\n *&#x2F;\nvoid PostOrder(BiTree T)&#123;\n    if(T!&#x3D;NULL)&#123;\n        PostOrder(T-&gt;lchild);\n        PostOrder(T-&gt;rchild);\n        putchar(T-&gt;data);\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"层次遍历\"><a href=\"#层次遍历\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"层次遍历\"></a>层次遍历</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>要进行层次遍历，需要借助一个队列，先将二叉树根结点入队，然后出队，访问该结点，若它有左子树，则将左子树根结点入队；若它有右子树，则将右子树根结点入队。然后出队，对出队结点访问，如此反复，直到队列为空。</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">&#x2F;*\n * 层次遍历，广度优先遍历\n *&#x2F;\nvoid LevelOrder(BiTree T)&#123;\n    LinkQueue Q;\n    InitQueue(Q);\n    BiTree p;\n    EnQueue(Q,T);\n    while (!IsEmpty(Q))&#123;\n        DeQueue(Q,p);\n        putchar(p-&gt;data);\n        if(p-&gt;lchild!&#x3D;NULL)&#123;\n            EnQueue(Q,p-&gt;lchild);\n        &#125;\n        if(p-&gt;rchild!&#x3D;NULL)&#123;\n            EnQueue(Q,p-&gt;rchild);\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n","text":"二叉树的定义typedef char BiElemType; typedef struct BiTNode&#123; BiElemType data; struct BiTNode *lchild,*rchild; &#125;BiTNode,*BiTree; &#x2F;&#...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%A0%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">二叉树的定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E5%BB%BA%E6%A0%91\"><span class=\"toc-text\">层次建树</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%88%E5%BA%8F%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">先序遍历</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%8F%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">中序遍历</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%90%8E%E5%BA%8F%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">后序遍历</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">层次遍历</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"数据结构代码实现：二叉树排序树","uid":"60c424b0116ca0c7f0541d6df3017fff","slug":"DataStructure-BST","date":"2020-05-17T01:33:21.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:15.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-BST.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200517093515.png","text":"二叉排序树的定义typedef int KeyType; typedef struct BSTNode&#123; KeyType key; struct BSTNode *lchild,*rchild; &#125;BSTNode,*BiTree; 插入操作 每次插入从根结点开...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.6k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"数据结构代码实现：队列的链式存储","uid":"c6398837a597d6503bc83e04065ac7ce","slug":"DataStructure-LinkQueue","date":"2020-05-12T01:21:11.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:26.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-LinkQueue.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200512092935.png","text":"队列的链式存储的定义#define ElemType int typedef struct LinkNode&#1